DistancePerRev_mm.linked: Distance in [mm] in one single revolution of the encoder-Bde-

InsideRange_mm.linked: For the Second Encoder on Erc both values must be within this tolerance-Bde-

LiftMastType.linked: Selection of the lifting mast. DZ Mast with free lift-Bde-Auswahl des Hubgerüstes. DZ Mast mit Freihub

MaxResolution_bits.linked: Resolution of the encoder in bits-Bde-

StepsPerRev.linked: Steps in one single revolution of the encoder-Bde-

BelowZeroThreshold_mm.linked: -Bde-Hubhöhenwert in mm unter Null der noch als in Ordnung toleriert wird.

EnableBelowZeroDetection.linked: -Bde-Wenn aktiv, wird die aktuelle Höhe im AutomatikMode auf deutliches Unterschreiten von 0 geprüft.

EnableOverHeightDetection.linked: If active, the current altitude in the automatic mode is compared with the MaximumForkHeight_mm and stopped if exceeded.-Bde-

MaximumNegativeSpeedChange_mms.linked: Affects the lowering speed, positioning accuracy is worse-Bde-

MaximumPositiveSpeedChange_mms.linked: Affects the lifting speed, positioning accuracy is worse-Bde-

RearSensorReactivationHeight_mm.linked: In combination with travel height 0 for ERC213a can activate PSS in load direction again-Bde-

ReducedNegativeSpeedChange_mms.linked: Reduced fork acceleration when lowering to prevent sensor stops by traversing the PSS field on Fast Flex-Bde-

UnlearnTime.linked: How long the eventcode will be shown on opt-Bde-

BeamLength_mm.linked: The Distance between Laser and ForkTip-Bde-Der Abstand zwischen Laser und ForkTip

ConstTargetSpeed_mms.linked: The speed with which the fork is moved during scanning-Bde-Die Geschwindigkeit, mit der die Gabel beim Scannen bewegt wird

DistanceForkTipToStack_mm.linked: Erc only. The Distance between Fork Tip and Pallet. Within ~ 10 cm.-Bde-

DistanceThroughStack_mm.linked: Pallet depth, the sensor must additionally see this length in order to be recognized as free-Bde-Palettentiefe, der Sensor muss diese Länge zusätzlich sehen, um als frei erkannt zu werden

LoadPosCheckAvailable.linked: Position check after unloading active-Bde-Nur Eks. Positionsprüfung nach dem Entladen aktiv

LoadPosCheckShortDistMulti.linked: How long the UnLoadCheck drives slowly. Multiplier x SlowDowndistance_mm-Bde-Wie lange der UnLoadCheck langsam fährt. Multiplikator x SlowDowndistance_mm

LoadPosCheckTipToBeFree.linked: Eks only. Number of sensors that must be free after to stop the unload procedure earlier. The fork will be moved down until the sensors are free, or the postion height is reached-Bde-Anzahl der Sensoren, die danach frei sein müssen, um den Entladevorgang früher zu beenden. Die Gabel wird nach unten bewegt, bis die Sensoren frei sind oder die Positionshöhe erreicht ist.

PalletOffset_mm.linked: Offset of the pallet in x-direction to the bottom pallet-Bde-Versatz der Palette in x-Richtung zur unteren Palette

RangeToBeEqual_mm.linked: The measured distance of both sensors must be within this window-Bde-Der gemessene Abstand beider Sensoren muss innerhalb dieses Fensters liegen

ReflectingHysteresis_mm.linked: Switching hysteresis, maximum up to the middle pallet foot-Bde-Schalthysterese, maximal bis zum mittleren Palettenfuß

StackingAvailable.linked: Pallet stack detection active-Bde-Nur Eks. Palettenstapel-Erkennung aktiv

zForkThickness_mm.linked: The max. thickness of the fork-Bde-Die maximale Dicke der Gabel

zLoadDistance_mm.linked: The distance between the fork and the recognized pallet base-Bde-Der Abstand zwischen der Gabel und der erkannten Palettenbasis

zMaxScanHeight_mm.linked: The max. Height that can be scanned. In addition there is 2 * zScanOffset_mm (for offset and braking distance)-Bde-Die max. Höhe, die gescannt werden kann. Zusätzlich gibt es 2 * zScanOffset_mm (für Offset und Bremsweg)

zPosLowerOffset_mm.linked: Distance between the lower inner laser point and the fork top-Bde-Abstand zwischen dem unteren inneren Laserpunkt und der Gabelspitze

zPosUpperOffset_mm.linked: Distance between the upper outer laser point and the fork top-Bde-Abstand zwischen dem oberen äußeren Laserpunkt und der Gabelspitze

zScanFilter_mm.linked: Every x mm in z-direction a measurement is used for error evaluation-Bde-Alle x mm in z-Richtung wird eine Messung zur Fehlerauswertung verwendet

zScanOffset_mm.linked: The offset in z-direction, which is still scanned after the supposed recognition of the upper edge of the pallet, in order to recognize further pallets-Bde-Der Versatz in z-Richtung, der nach der vermeintlichen Erkennung der Palettenoberkante noch gescannt wird, um weitere Paletten zu erkennen

zScanStartHeight_mm.linked: Start height for the pallet scan-Bde-Starthöhe für den Palettenscan

zToleranceWindow_mm.linked: If, after the scan, the fork is at any height, and that height is within stack height plus excavation plus this value, no new altitude will be approached-Bde-Wenn sich die Gabel nach dem Scan auf einer beliebigen Höhe befindet und diese Höhe innerhalb der Stapelhöhe plus Aushub plus diesem Wert liegt, wird keine neue Höhe angefahren

RevokeSignalTime.linked: Timespan for which the revoke signal will be sent to the external safety PLC. Minimum is 200ms.-Bde-

SteerTeachTolerance_cdeg.linked: Tolerance range around 0 degrees in which the actual steering angle has to be during teaching-Bde-

SteerTeachtoleranceHoldTime.linked: Timespan for which the steering angle has to remain in the tolerance range during teaching-Bde-

TeachModeOnSignalTime.linked: Timespan for which the teach mode on signal will be sent to the external safety PLC. Minimum is 200ms.-Bde-

TeachRetries.linked: Number of times the teaching process is retried if unsuccessful-Bde-

TeachSignalTime.linked: Timespan for which the teach signal will be sent to the external safety PLC. Minimum is 200ms.-Bde-

TeachTimeout.linked: Timeout for waiting for external signal during teaching, e.g. waiting for steering to reach the tolerance or reaction of safety PLC or vehicle to teach signal-Bde-

FlexlineOffset_mm.linked: Offset in measurement value between Flexline and Pallet Breaking Sensors. This value will be subtracted from the actually measured value, doesn't have to be negative (Default 2160-Bde-

ForkTipSensorCount.linked: Eks only. Number of fork sensors to be evaluated. At FourOfFour, every sensor has to recognize something to stop the vehicle. With stacking activatet, the max. is internally limited to TwoOfFour-Bde-Nur Eks. Anzahl der auszuwertenden Gabelsensoren. Bei FourOfFour muss jeder Sensor etwas erkennen, um das Fahrzeug anzuhalten. Bei aktivierter Stapelung ist das Maximum intern auf TwoOfFour begrenzt.

ForkTipSensorType.linked: Used fork sensor type, so that the correct measuring range is used-Bde-

PalletDistancePowerOffPostRun.linked: Delay before switching off pallet distance sensor after no pallet has been detected-Bde-

PlausibilityCheckEnable.linked: Load handling plausibility check using the analogue pallet sensor-Bde-

PlausibilityEnable_mm.linked: This length depends on the installed fork. If the measured values are larger, the process will not start.-Bde-

PlausibilityExit_mm.linked: Counter part to PlausibilityEnable_mm, distance to compare measured value with odometry while exiting the station-Bde-

PlausibilityHysteresis_mm.linked: If the delta is greater between the distance traveled and the distance measured with the sensor, the pallet is pushed-Bde-

StationExitDistanceForRearSensor_mm.linked: In case feature is enabled via sensor mask: Distance during which rear sensors will be evaluated even when driving in drive-direction-Bde-

SpecialFunctionsConfiguration.linked: Track surveying, Dryer, LinearAxis, RGB Underfloorlight-Bde-

ErrorPulseRate.linked: Duration at which additional clamp lights are flashing in case of an error-Bde-

LostSwitch.linked: Debounce during automatic travel, where an end switch is allowed to change, before an error is generated-Bde-

MovedBeyondLimit.linked: Debounce for reaching either end switch while still allowing a raise/lower command before an error is generated-Bde-

ReachedLowerEnd.linked: Debounce for reaching lower end switch without also having a is-clamped signal before an error is generated-Bde-

TransitionDelay.linked: Delay between changing operating states before being able to control the clamp again is possible-Bde-

EnableQuickDrop.linked: Finish drop operation without clompletely opening the clamp-Bde-

ForkHeightCheck.linked: When active, clip action is only possible when the fork is on the SafetyHeight.-Bde-

Implementation.linked: Select which type of active clamp is to be used Default (EActiveClampImplementation_None)-Bde-

Laufzeit.linked: The time after which an end stop should be reached-Bde-

LoadPalletCheck.linked: When active SemiAutoMatik Clamps only possible with Pallet Available-Bde-

maxDistance.linked: Maximum distance at which the car can stand-Bde-

minDistance.linked: Minimum distance at which the car can stand-Bde-

SafetyHeight.linked: Height in which the fork must be in order to open the clamp in automatic mode. Must correspond to the height specified when clamping in the stations.-Bde-

ShowPosition.linked: Shows the current hold-down position via the up / down button-Bde-

SwitchBackToFork.linked: The time after the manual mode, after releasing the drawbar, the fork can be moved again.-Bde-

ValveOffDelay.linked: After stopping the pump, it will still turn for about 250 to 500ms. As long as the valves must remain open.-Bde-

PwmSteps.linked: Number of levels that are possible, 2ms Fast Task and 20ms cycle-Bde-

TrailerLiftWaitDelay.linked: Time after which the lift is assumed to be finished on compressed air trailers.-Bde-

TrailerType.linked: Select the correct trailer, Shooter has additional flag in Cvc SensorMask.-Bde-
